      "Data Component": "Application Log Content",
      "Detects": "<p>Monitor application logs for activity that may highlight malicious attempts to access application data, especially abnormal search activity targeting passwords and other artifacts related to credentials.<span onclick=\"scrollToRef('scite-3')\" id=\"scite-ref-3-a\" class=\"scite-citeref-number\" title=\"Slack Help Center. (n.d.). View Access Logs for your workspace. Retrieved April 10, 2023.\" data-reference=\"Slack Help Center Access Logs\"><sup><a href=\"https://slack.com/help/articles/360002084807-View-Access-Logs-for-your-workspace\" target=\"_blank\" data-hasqtip=\"2\" aria-describedby=\"qtip-2\">[3]</a></sup></span></p>"
